    ],
    "text": "Suspect Arrested with a Large Stock of Kerala Cannabis \u2013 Kayts Police",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      515.56,
      518.02,
      595.57
    ],
    "text": "Officers of the Kayts Police, together with personnel of the Sri Lanka Navy and the Police Special Bureau, conducted a raid at Suruvil Beach within the Kayts Police Division on the afternoon of 04.03.2026. During the operation, a suspect was arrested in possession of approximately 368 kilograms of Kerala cannabis.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      610.15,
      430.81,
      625.69
    ],
    "text": "The arrested suspect is a 34-year-old resident of Velanai.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      640.15,
      516.82,
      671.89
    ],
    "text": "Preliminary investigations indicate that the stock of Kerala cannabis had been smuggled into the country from India by a fishing vessel.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      686.35,
      469.33,
      701.89
    ],
    "text": "Further investigations are being carried out by the Kayts Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
